OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FThe arrest warrant is being seen as
OL,8,Fpart of President Trump's ramping up
OL,9,Fof pressure on Cuba's communist
OL,10,Fgovernment, as ITV News US
OL,11,FCorrespondent Dan Rivers reports
OL,13,FFormer president of Cuba, Raul Castro,
OL,14,Fhas been charged by the US over the
OL,15,F1996 downing of two civilian planes.
OL,17,FFour people, three of them Americans,
OL,18,Fwere killed in the attack by two Cuban
OL,19,FMiG fighters in international airspace.
OL,26,@kD@ZrzuD@]rz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
