OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FThe US says the charges relate to
OL,8,FCastro's alleged role as defence
OL,9,Fminister in ordering the downing of
OL,10,Fthe two civilian planes, which
OL,11,Fbelonged to the Brothers to the Rescue
OL,12,Fgroup, founded by Cuban exiles.
OL,14,FThe arrest warrant is seen as part of
OL,15,FPresident Donald Trump's ramping up of
OL,16,Fpressure on Cuba's communist
OL,17,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@kD@Zrz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FThe US has been threatening military
OL,8,Faction for months following the US
OL,9,Fcapture of Cuba's ally, Venezuelan
OL,10,FPresident Nicolas Maduro.
OL,12,FCastro - the brother of then-President
OL,13,FFidel Castro, and his defence minister
OL,14,F- faces charges including murder and
OL,15,Fdestruction of an aeroplane.
OL,17,FActing Attorney General Todd Blanche
OL,18,Fannounced the charges at a ceremony on
OL,19,FWednesday, honouring the victims on a
OL,20,Fday that Cuban exiles celebrate as
OL,21,FCuba's independence day.
OL,26,@kD@ZrzrD@Prp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FIt follows a US-imposed blockade of
OL,8,FCuba that choked off fuel shipments to
OL,9,Fthe Caribbean nation, leading to
OL,10,Fsevere blackouts, food shortages and
OL,11,Fan economic collapse across the island.
OL,13,FThat followed the capture of Cuba's
OL,14,Flongtime patron Maduro by US forces in
OL,15,FJanuary this year, which authorities
OL,16,Fjustified by citing drug-trafficking
OL,17,Fcharges indicted by Trump's first
OL,18,Fadministration.
OL,26,@kD@Zrz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FWith the Venezuelan leader awaiting
OL,8,Ftrial in New York, Trump has been
OL,9,Fratcheting up talk of regime change in
OL,10,FCuba.
OL,12,FEarlier this year, the US president
OL,13,Fthreatened to conduct a "friendly
OL,14,Ftakeover" of the country if the
OL,15,Fleadership did not open its economy to
OL,16,FAmerican investment and kick out
OL,17,Fadversaries of the US.
OL,26,@kD@Zrz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, US Secretary of State
OL,8,FMarco Rubio urged the Cuban people to
OL,9,Fdemand a free-market economy with new
OL,10,Fleadership that he said will chart a
OL,11,Fnew course in relations with the US.
OL,13,F"In the US, we are ready to open a new
OL,14,Fchapter in the relationship between
OL,15,Four people," Rubio, the son of Cuban
OL,16,Fimmigrants, said in a Spanish-language
OL,17,Fvideo message.
OL,19,F"Currently, the only thing standing in
OL,20,Fthe way of a better future is those
OL,21,Fwho control your country."
OL,26,@kD@ZrzuD@AOUwD@LO]{D@AOU}D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FCuba's deputy foreign minister, Carlos
OL,8,FF. de Cossio, lashed out at Rubio on
OL,9,FX, saying he "lies so repeatedly and
OL,10,Funscrupulously about Cuba and tries to
OL,11,Fjustify the aggression he inflicts on
OL,12,Fthe Cuban people".
OL,14,FRubio "knows full well that there is
OL,15,Fno excuse for such cruel and ruthless
OL,16,Faggression," he added.
OL,18,FCastro took over as president from his
OL,19,Failing brother, Fidel Castro, in 2006,
OL,20,Fbefore handing power to trusted
OL,21,Floyalist Diaz-Canel in 2018.
OL,26,@kD@ZrzpD@KrtqD@NOUtD@QO]xD@LO]}D@Krt
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
