FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FWhile he retired in 2021 as head of
OL,8,Fthe Cuban Communist Party, he is
OL,9,Fwidely believed to wield power behind
OL,10,Fthe scenes, underscored by the
OL,11,Fprominence of his grandson, Raul
OL,12,FGuillermo Rodriguez Castro, who
OL,13,Fpreviously met secretly with Rubio.
OL,15,FLast week, CIA Director John Ratcliffe
OL,16,Ftravelled to Havana for meetings with
OL,17,FCuban officials, including Castro's
OL,18,Fgrandson. Two other senior State
OL,19,FDepartment officials met with the
OL,20,Fgrandson in April.
OL,26,@kD@ZrzsD@_rztD@Ort
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
