PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FThere's no indication that Castro will
OL,8,Fbe taken into US custody anytime soon.
OL,10,FHowever, the "symbolic nature" of the
OL,11,Fcharges is "absolutely crucial", said
OL,12,FLindsey Lazopoulos Friedman, a former
OL,13,Fprosecutor at the US attorney's office
OL,14,Fin Miami who handled national security
OL,15,Fcases and crimes involving Cubans.
OL,26,@kD@Zrz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
