FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,F"Even though Raul Castro will likely
OL,8,Fstay and die in Cuba, you can use the
OL,9,Findictment as a pressure point, a
OL,10,Ftactical advantage, to extract other
OL,11,Fconcessions like the release of
OL,12,Fprisoners or to keep Russia out," she
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FWhat happened to the two Brothers to
OL,16,Fthe Rescue planes?
OL,26,@kD@ZrzoD@AOUoD@PrztD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
