PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FStarting in 1995, planes flown by
OL,8,Fmembers of Brothers to the Rescue, a
OL,9,Fgroup founded by Cuban exiles, flew
OL,10,Fover Havana dropping leaflets urging
OL,11,FCubans to rise up against the Castro
OL,12,Fgovernment.
OL,14,FThe Cubans protested to the US
OL,15,Fgovernment, warning that they would
OL,16,Fdefend their airspace.
OL,26,@kD@Zrz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
