FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779318188
OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,FFederal Aviation Administration
OL,8,Fofficials also opened an investigation
OL,9,Fand met with the group's leaders to
OL,10,Furge them to ground the flights,
OL,11,Faccording to declassified government
OL,12,Frecords obtained by George Washington
OL,13,FUniversity's National Security Archive.
OL,15,F"This latest overflight can only be
OL,16,Fseen as further taunting of the Cuban
OL,17,FGovernment," an FAA official wrote in
OL,18,Fan email to her superiors after one
OL,19,Fintrusion in January 1996.
OL,26,@kD@ZrzwD@AOUyD@LO]
