OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,F"Worst case scenario is that one of
OL,8,Fthese days the Cubans will shoot down
OL,9,Fone of these planes."
