OL,3,CFormer Cuban president Raul Castro
OL,4,Ccharged in US over 1996 downing of two
OL,5,Cplanes
OL,7,F"Three US citizens and one legal
OL,8,Fpermanent resident were killed in a
OL,9,Fpremeditated, orchestrated murder.
OL,10,FThat should never be forgotten."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
